quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf. Mi woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden
  50,2,"Si ko woni, Й“e ЕӢalЙ—u ko tawi kon jertinoowo arii Й“e iwЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e ; heeferЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko huunde haawniinde"
  50,3,"Kere si men maayii, men wontii mbulmbuldi...? ЖҠum Й—on ko ruttitagol woЙ—Й—ungol non"
  50,4,GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en anndi ko leydi ndin Гұaamata kon e maЙ“Й“e ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenunde
  50,5,"Si ko woni, Й“e fennu goonga kan tuma nde ka arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e e nder fiyaaku jilЙ“uЙ—o"
  50,6,"E Й“ee ndaaraali kammu ngun dow maЙ“Й“e, ko honno Men mahiri ngun Men cuЙ—ini ngu ; hara perЙ—i alanaa ngu"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fuЙ—ini e mayri kala nooneeji [puЙ—i] wooЙ—uЙ—i"
  50,8,fii tasakuyee e waaju wonannde kala jeyaaЙ—o ruttotooЙ—o
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam barkinaaЙ—am ummaade ka kammu, Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am gese e gabbe soГұeteeЙ—e"
  50,10,e leЙ—Й—e tamaro juutuЙ—e wonduЙ—e e piindi fawondirndi
  50,11,ko arsike jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. Men wuurnitiri Й—am kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko non woni fii ummital ngal
  50,12,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e nuuhu Й“en, e yimЙ“e ЖҒunndu Й“en e Samuuda'en [fow] fennuno"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musiЙ—Й“e Luutu Й“en"
  50,14,"e yimЙ“e fitaare nden, e yimЙ“e Tubba' Й“en. Kala maЙ“Й“e fennuno NulaaЙ“e Й“en, kammbaa Am on jojji"
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno fii tagu aranu ngun? Ko woni kamЙ“e, hiЙ“e e jiЙ“aare fii tagiteede laawol kesol"
  50,16,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii neЙ—Й—anke on, MeЙ—en anndi ko wonkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Menen Й“uri Й“adaade mo e dii Й—aЙ—ol (makko) daande ngol"
  50,17,"tuma nde jaЙ“Й“oytooЙ“e Й“en Й—iЙ—o jaЙ“Й“oroytoo [golle makko Й—en] Гұaamo e nano, hara hiЙ“e jooЙ—ii"
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wanaa hino takko makko winndoowo tawaaЙ—o"
  50,19,"ЖҠeЙ—Й—ere maayde nden ardi e goonga : \"Ko Й—um wonunoo ko dogaynoЙ—aa"
  50,20,Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni Г‘alaande kammbaa nden
  50,21,"Wonkii kala ara, hara hiki wonndi e soggoowo e seedotooЙ—o"
  50,22,GomЙ—ii a laatinoke welsindiiЙ—o e ndee. Men hunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa Й—en hannde ko seeЙ“uЙ—e
  50,23,"WonndiiЙ—o makko on wi'a: \"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ka am Й—oo, maandinaa-Й—um"
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon Й—iЙ—o, kala yedduЙ—o canndallo"
  50,25,"haЙ—oowo moЖҙЖҙere, jaggitoowo, sikkitiiЙ—o"
  50,26,on waЙ—iduЙ—o e Allah reweteeЙ—o goo. Bugee mo ka nder lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere woЙ—Й—unde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am Й—oo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol waЙ—titetaake ka Am Й—oo ; Mi siforaa kadi tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en
  50,30,"Г‘alnde Men wi'anoyta Jahannama on : \"E a heewii?\" Nge wi'a: \"Ko Й“eydee hino woodi"
  50,31,"Aljanna on Й“aЙ—tinanee gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, hara wanaa ka woЙ—Й—i"
  50,32,"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ko fodaЙ—on, wonannde kala ruttiiЙ—o [e Joomi mun] reeniiЙ—o"
  50,33,"on huluЙ—o Jom Hinaranke On ka wirnii, o ardi e Й“ernde laaЙ“unde"
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam\". Ko nden woni Гұalaande luttaynde nden"
  50,35,"Hino woodani Й“e ton kala ko Й“e faaletee, hara kadi Й“eydaari hino ka Amen"
  50,36,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e gire Й—en Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“en Й“urnooЙ“e doole, Й“en wanngorii e leydi ndin, ndaarugol taw si Й“e heЙ“ay laaworde"
  50,37,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um, waaju wonannde kala jom Й“ernde, maa tuЙ—uЙ—o noppi hara ko tawaaЙ—o"
  50,38,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, nder balЙ—e jeegoo, tampere woo heЙ“aali Men. @Corrected"
  50,39,"MuГұГұo e ko Й“e wowlata kon, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Joomi maa ado puЙ—al naange ngen e ado mutal ngal"
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Mo e ka battane [julЙ—e] farlaaЙ—e"
  50,41,"HeЙ—o, Гұalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e nokkuure Й“adiinde"
  50,42,"Гұalnde Й“e naniroyta haacaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko nden woni Г‘alnnde yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]"
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Menen wuurnata Men wara, ko ka Amen kadi woni ruttorde nden"
  50,44,"Г‘alnde leydi ndin seekotoo [Й“e yaltira] heГұagol; ko nde woni mooЙ“irde newaniinde Men"
  50,45,"Ko Menen Й“uri anndude ko Й“e wowlata kon. A wonaa dooloowoЙ“e. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala huloowo kammbaa An on"